  $manifest = Get-Content -LiteralPath (Join-Path $backupRoot 'backup-manifest.json') -Raw | ConvertFrom-Json
  (($manifest | Where-Object { -not (Test-Path -LiteralPath $_.Backup) }).Count -eq 0) -and ($manifest.Count -gt 0)
  ~~~
  Expected output: `True`.
  Diagnostic checks: Compare `$manifest.Count` to the expected number of real Codex duplicate folders.
  Error recovery: If any backup path is missing, stop and rerun backup for the missing item before continuing.

